import { format, subDays } from 'date-fns'; import numeral from 'numeral'; import { Box, Card, CardHeader, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableRow, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'; const transactions = [ { id: 'd46800328cd510a668253b45', amount: 25000, currency: 'usd', date: new Date(), sender: 'Devias', type: 'receive' }, { id: 'b4b19b21656e44b487441c50', amount: 6843, currency: 'usd', date: subDays(new Date(), 1), sender: 'Zimbru', type: 'send' }, { id: '56c09ad91f6d44cb313397db', amount: 91823, currency: 'usd', date: subDays(new Date(), 1), sender: 'Vertical Jelly', type: 'send' }, { id: 'aaeb96c5a131a55d9623f44d', amount: 49550, currency: 'usd', date: subDays(new Date(), 3), sender: 'Devias', type: 'receive' } ]; const OverviewLatestTransactions = (props) => ( {transactions.map((transaction) => ( {format(transaction.date, 'LLL').toUpperCase()} {format(transaction.date, 'd')}
{transaction.sender} {transaction.type === 'receive' ? 'Payment received' : 'Payment sent'}
{transaction.type === 'receive' ? '+' : '-'} {' '} {numeral(transaction.amount).format('$0,0.00')} {transaction.currency.toUpperCase()} ))}
); export default OverviewLatestTransactions;
